{"article_id":"qlG8YnydUXNJPlkG","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"President Obama has received a much-anticipated classified report on alleged Russian and other foreign meddling in American elections ,","depth":4},{"id":1,"text":"heightening interest in what evidence the file contains","depth":5},{"id":2,"text":"as Republicans spar over the cyberattack claims","depth":6},{"id":3,"text":"-","depth":7},{"id":4,"text":"and wait for their chance","depth":8},{"id":5,"text":"to see the findings themselves .","depth":8},{"id":6,"text":"Director of National Intelligence James Clapper and other top intelligence officials visited the White House Thursday afternoon ,","depth":6},{"id":7,"text":"to brief the president on the materials .","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"President-elect Donald Trump is to be briefed on the report on Friday .","depth":5},{"id":9,"text":"Clapper also testified before the Senate Armed Services Committee","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"that they plan to brief Congress","depth":7},{"id":11,"text":"and release an unclassified version of the report to the public \" early next week .","depth":7},{"id":12,"text":"\" In its earlier assessment , the intelligence community said","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"Moscow interfered in the election","depth":8},{"id":14,"text":"to help Trump win .","depth":8},{"id":15,"text":"`` We stand actually more resolutely on the strength of that statement","depth":8},{"id":16,"text":"than we did on the 7th of October , ''","depth":8},{"id":17,"text":"Clapper said .","depth":7},{"id":18,"text":"The administration ' s allegations of Russia-directed hacking of Democratic organizations during the 2016 U.S. elections","depth":5},{"id":19,"text":"- and punitive measures","depth":6},{"id":20,"text":"taken against Russian officials and agencies last week -","depth":6},{"id":21,"text":"continue to drive fierce debate in Washington , especially among Republicans .","depth":4},{"id":22,"text":"Trump and his allies have cast doubt on the claims .","depth":6},{"id":23,"text":"The latest detail","depth":11},{"id":24,"text":"to raise questions","depth":11},{"id":25,"text":"is confirmation from the Democratic National Committee","depth":11},{"id":26,"text":"that the FBI did not examine their servers .","depth":11},{"id":27,"text":"A spokesman confirmed to Fox News","depth":10},{"id":28,"text":"that \" the FBI never requested access to the DNC 's computer servers , \"","depth":11},{"id":29,"text":"though the DNC had several meetings with FBI and other officials during the investigation .","depth":11},{"id":30,"text":"BuzzFeed first reported","depth":10},{"id":31,"text":"the FBI did not inspect the servers","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"before issuing their report .","depth":11},{"id":33,"text":"That 13-page report ,","depth":12},{"id":34,"text":"issued with the Department of Homeland Security ,","depth":12},{"id":35,"text":"also has faced some scrutiny","depth":11},{"id":36,"text":"for being light on hard evidence","depth":11},{"id":37,"text":"confirming Russian government involvement .","depth":11},{"id":38,"text":"The report","depth":9},{"id":39,"text":"sent to Obama","depth":10},{"id":40,"text":"- and soon to be shared with Trump and others -","depth":10},{"id":41,"text":"could offer more .","depth":8},{"id":42,"text":"Trump tweeted earlier this week","depth":7},{"id":43,"text":"that it was \" very strange \"","depth":8},{"id":44,"text":"his briefing on Russia hacking will not be held until Friday .","depth":8},{"id":45,"text":"He speculated ,","depth":8},{"id":46,"text":"\" perhaps more time","depth":9},{"id":47,"text":"needed","depth":10},{"id":48,"text":"to build a case. \"","depth":10},{"id":49,"text":"Intelligence officials said","depth":8},{"id":50,"text":"there had been no delay .","depth":8},{"id":51,"text":"Trump also has drawn attention to WikiLeaks founder Julian Assange ' s recent interview on Fox News ' \" Hannity \"","depth":7},{"id":52,"text":"in which Assange insisted","depth":8},{"id":53,"text":"the Russians were not his source for thousands of hacked emails from Hillary Clinton campaign chairman John Podesta .","depth":8},{"id":54,"text":"Some Republicans , though , have made clear","depth":9},{"id":55,"text":"they harbor few doubts about Russia ' s cyber-meddling","depth":9},{"id":56,"text":"-- and do not see Assange as a reliable source .","depth":8},{"id":57,"text":"Senate Armed Services Committee Chairman John McCain , R-Ariz. , said at Thursday ' s hearing","depth":9},{"id":58,"text":"that he believes","depth":11},{"id":59,"text":"Assange is responsible","depth":11},{"id":60,"text":"for publishing names of individuals","depth":12},{"id":61,"text":"who work with the U.S. government","depth":12},{"id":62,"text":"and putting them at risk .","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"Clapper said ,","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"\" Yes , he has , \"","depth":10},{"id":65,"text":"adding","depth":10},{"id":66,"text":"that he does not find Assange to be credible .","depth":10},{"id":67,"text":"McCain also said Thursday","depth":9},{"id":68,"text":"that `` every American should be alarmed '' by Russia 's alleged meddling in the 2016 presidential election .","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"There is `` no escaping the fact","depth":10},{"id":70,"text":"that this committee meets today for the first time in this new Congress in the aftermath of an unprecedented attack on our democracy , ''","depth":10},{"id":71,"text":"he said .","depth":9},{"id":72,"text":"In prepared testimony Thursday , intelligence officials said","depth":9},{"id":73,"text":"Russia poses a major and growing threat to U.S. government , military , diplomatic and commercial operations","depth":10},{"id":74,"text":"-- as well as America 's critical infrastructure .","depth":10},{"id":75,"text":"Russia is among at least 30 nations","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"that are developing capabilities","depth":11},{"id":77,"text":"to launch cyberattacks ,","depth":11},{"id":78,"text":"according to their statement .","depth":9},{"id":79,"text":"Clapper on Thursday stood by claims","depth":8},{"id":80,"text":"that the Russian government was involved in the 2016 hacking .","depth":8},{"id":81,"text":"In new tweets early Thursday , Trump backed away from Assange somewhat .","depth":8},{"id":82,"text":"He blamed the `` dishonest media ''","depth":9},{"id":83,"text":"for portraying him as agreeing with Assange .","depth":9},{"id":84,"text":"Accusations","depth":4},{"id":85,"text":"Russia interfered in the 2016 election","depth":5},{"id":86,"text":"by hacking Democratic email accounts","depth":5},{"id":87,"text":"have roiled Washington for weeks .","depth":3},{"id":88,"text":"Obama struck back at Moscow in late December with penalties","depth":6},{"id":89,"text":"aimed at Russia 's leading spy agencies , the GRU and FSB ,","depth":8},{"id":90,"text":"that","depth":10},{"id":91,"text":"the U.S. said","depth":10},{"id":92,"text":"were involved .","depth":9},{"id":93,"text":"The GRU is Russia 's military intelligence agency .","depth":8},{"id":94,"text":"The FSB is the main successor to the Soviet-era KGB .","depth":8},{"id":95,"text":"But Trump easily could rescind the sanctions .","depth":6},{"id":96,"text":"So far , he has publicly refused to accept the conclusion","depth":8},{"id":97,"text":"that Russia is responsible for the attacks .","depth":8},{"id":98,"text":"Trump suggested Wednesday in a tweet","depth":8},{"id":99,"text":"that one of Russia 's primary targets , the Democratic National Committee , could be to blame","depth":9},{"id":100,"text":"for being `` so careless . ''","depth":9},{"id":101,"text":"CIA Director John Brennan said in a Dec. 16 message to employees","depth":6},{"id":102,"text":"that the FBI agreed with the agency 's conclusion","depth":7},{"id":103,"text":"that Russia 's goal was to support Trump in the election .","depth":7},{"id":104,"text":"Brennan wrote","depth":6},{"id":105,"text":"that he also had spoken with Clapper","depth":7},{"id":106,"text":"and said","depth":8},{"id":107,"text":"`` there is strong consensus among us on the scope , nature , and intent of Russian interference in our presidential election . ''","depth":8},{"id":108,"text":"Moscow has denied the hacking allegations","depth":5},{"id":109,"text":"and dismissed Obama 's sanctions as an attempt","depth":6},{"id":110,"text":"to `` harm Russian-American ties . ''","depth":6},{"id":111,"text":"Although Russian President Vladimir Putin rebuked the Obama administration","depth":6},{"id":112,"text":"for trying to punish Russia ,","depth":6},{"id":113,"text":"he said","depth":6},{"id":114,"text":"his country would not immediately retaliate","depth":7},{"id":115,"text":"and would instead wait for a new U.S. approach","depth":8},{"id":116,"text":"after Trump takes office .","depth":8}],"relations":[{"parent":233,"left":200,"right":232,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":200,"left":134,"right":199,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":134,"left":122,"right":133,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":122,"left":0,"right":121,"relation":"causal","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":121,"left":1,"right":120,"relation":"context","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":120,"left":2,"right":119,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":119,"left":3,"right":118,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":118,"left":4,"right":5,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":133,"left":124,"right":132,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":124,"left":123,"right":8,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":123,"left":6,"right":7,"relation":"purpose","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":132,"left":126,"right":131,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":126,"left":9,"right":125,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":125,"left":10,"right":11,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":131,"left":128,"right":130,"relation":"elaboration","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":128,"left":12,"right":127,"relation":"att